              </svg>
            </div>
            CI/CD Integration
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-base-content/70">
            <p class="flex-auto">Built-in GitHub Action support. Integrate consistency checks directly into your development workflow.</p>
          </dd>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-base-content">
            <div class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            Lightning Fast
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-base-content/70">
            <p class="flex-auto">Built with Rust for maximum performance. Check thousands of links in milliseconds.</p>
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Getting Started Section -->
<section class="py-24 sm:py-32 bg-base-200">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-base-content sm:text-4xl">
        Get Started in Minutes
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-base-content/70">
        Configure Clevis with a simple TOML file and start checking consistency immediately.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <!-- Installation -->
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-xl">1. Install Clevis</h3>
            <div class="mockup-code">
              <pre><code># Download from GitHub Releases
curl -L https://github.com/jesse-c/clevis/releases/latest/download/clevis-linux -o clevis
chmod +x clevis</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Configuration -->
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-xl">2. Create Config</h3>
            <div class="mockup-code">
              <pre><code># clevis.toml
[[links]]
name = "version-sync"
a.toml.path = "Cargo.toml"
a.toml.key = "package.version"
b.toml.path = "docs/package.json"
b.toml.key = "version"</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Usage -->
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-xl">3. Check Consistency</h3>
            <div class="mockup-code">
              <pre><code># Check all links
clevis check

# Check specific link
clevis check version-sync

# List all configured links
clevis list</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="bg-primary">
  <div class="px-6 py-24 sm:px-6 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
        Ready to keep your code in sync?
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-white/90">
        Join developers who trust Clevis to maintain consistency across their codebases.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
        <a href="https://github.com/jesse-c/clevis" class="btn btn-lg bg-white text-primary hover:bg-gray-100 border-0">
          Get Started
        </a>
        <a href={~p"/example"} class="btn btn-lg btn-outline text-white border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-primary">
